datasets.name: 4ebc6801
datasets.displayName: DataTable User, Notebook and Query Counts
datasets.query:
select
  datatable,
  count(distinct email) as user_count,
  count(distinct notebookid) as notebooks,
  count(distinct commandid) as queries,
  min(event_date) as earliest_date,
  max(event_date) as latest_date
FROM
  edav_prd_cdh.cdh_engineering_etl.product_analytics_cube
where
  :date_min <= event_date
  and event_date <= :date_max
group by
  datatable
having
  count(distinct notebookid) >= :min_notebooks
order by
  queries desc

datasets.name: 157c0c8c
datasets.query:
select
  min(event_date) as earliest_date,
  max(event_date) as most_recent_date,
  count(distinct event_date) as execution_counts,
  notebookid,
  concat('https://adb-5189663741904016.16.azuredatabricks.net/editor/notebooks/',notebookid) as notebook_url,
  round(sum(execution_time), 1) as total_execution_time,
  round(avg(execution_time), 1) as avg_execution_time,
  round(stddev(execution_time), 2) as stddev_execution_time,
  max(commandtext) as commandtext,
  max(table_count) as table_count,
  max(column_count) as column_count,
  max(tables) as tables,
  max(columns) as columns
from
  edav_prd_cdh.cdh_engineering_etl.product_analytics_cube_collected_columns
where
  :date_min <= event_date
  and event_date <= :date_max
group by notebookid
order by avg_execution_time desc,
  execution_counts desc,
  total_execution_time desc

  count(distinct commandid) as queries,
  min(event_date) as earliest_date,

FROM
  edav_prd_cdh.cdh_engineering_etl.product_analytics_cube

datasets.name: 701a1d04
datasets.displayName: Table Columns unused based on current usage
datasets.query:
select
  concat(s.table_schema,'.',s.table_name) as datatable,
  max(u.event_date) as most_recent_use,
  count(distinct s.column_name) as column_count,
  column_count - count(distinct u.column_name) as count_unused,
  if(column_count=count_unused,True,False) as table_unused,
  round(count_unused/column_count*100,1) as percent_unused,
  array_intersect(collect_set(u.column_name), collect_set(s.column_name) ) as unused_columns,
  collect_set(s.column_name) as all_columns
from
  edav_prd_cdh.information_schema.columns s
    left join edav_prd_cdh.cdh_engineering_etl.product_analytics_cube u
      on s.table_schema = u.table_schema
      and s.table_name = u.table_name
      and s.column_name = u.column_name
where s.table_schema in 
  ('cdh_truveta','cdh_truveta_lava',
  'cdh_premier_lava_dev', 'cdh_premier_v2',
  'cdh_premier_lava','cdh_premier_lava_dev')
group by
  s.table_schema,
  s.table_name
order by
  count_unused desc --  ) x

widget.textbox_spec:
### Product Analytics Documentation

**Product Analytics** data tables are built every morning from two core system sources, notebook usage and table/column Delta lineage:
* **[SILVER_USAGE_TBL](https://adb-5189663741904016.16.azuredatabricks.net/explore/data/edav_prd_cdh/cdh_engineering_etl/analytics_cluster_silver?o=5189663741904016&activeTab=lineage)** - daily snapshot of usage from EDAV audit logs
* **[CORE_USAGE_TBL](https://adb-5189663741904016.16.azuredatabricks.net/explore/data/edav_prd_cdh/cdh_engineering_etl/product_analytics_core_usage?o=5189663741904016&activeTab=lineage)** - core usage table at notebookid/commandid level with commandtext, clusterid, (user) email, event_date, and (rounded) runtime
* **[CORE_USAGE_TBL_GROUPED](https://adb-5189663741904016.16.azuredatabricks.net/explore/data/edav_prd_cdh/cdh_engineering_etl/product_analytics_core_usage?o=5189663741904016&activeTab=lineage)** - core usage table at notebookid/commandid level with clusterid, (user) email, event_date, and (rounded) runtime (no commandtext)
* **[EDAV_LINEAGE_TBL](https://adb-5189663741904016.16.azuredatabricks.net/explore/data/edav_project_audit_logs/cdh/column_lineage?o=5189663741904016)** - Databricks Delta Column level Lineage Table at notebookid level
* **[ANALYTICS_TBL](https://adb-5189663741904016.16.azuredatabricks.net/explore/data/edav_prd_cdh/cdh_engineering_etl/product_analytics_cube?o=5189663741904016&activeTab=lineage)** - Product Analytics primary table, as an inner Join of CORE_USAGE_TBL and EDAV_LINEAGE_TBL by notebookid with column match
* **[ANALYTICS_TBL_GROUPED](https://adb-5189663741904016.16.azuredatabricks.net/explore/data/edav_prd_cdh/cdh_engineering_etl/product_analytics_core_usage_grouped?o=5189663741904016&activeTab=lineage)** - ANALYTICS_TBL at the notebookid level
